item.title: SoftLayer_Account_Shipment_Tracking_Data
item.description: SoftLayer_Account_Shipment_Tracking_Data Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Account_Shipment_Tracking_Data data type contains information on a single piece of tracking information pertaining to a shipment. This tracking information tracking numbers by which the shipment may be tracked through the shipping courier. Local createUserId The create user id of the tracking data. Type: integer id The unique id of the tracking data. Type: integer modifyUserId The user id of the tracking data.
